{"tid":2318522,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"建興大廈其實喺香港嘅地下維穩機器","createTime":"2020-12-09T11:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T08:51:53.000Z","uid":330057,"like":46,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"74ff5240c66cd6ce3b0663b2042ee37915ddcad1","tid":2318522,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"如果冇咗建興大廈，犯罪率大大提升<br />\n強姦犯冇咗地方發洩，魔手即刻伸向民間婦女<br />\n由國際金融中心即刻變咗強姦之都！<br />\n仲癲過印度。<br />\n而實際上香港嘅繁榮安定都係由建興大廈暗地裏位置<br />\n當年中國啱啱接手香港<br />\n第一任警務處長甚至有諗過要將警察訓練營搬去建興大廈。可惜最後冇咁做到。<br />\n大家試諗吓，一旦建興大廈呢個地方俾人清場<br />\n啲強姦犯即刻暴走周圍強姦人<br />\n即使係禮賓府都唔會例外<br />\n鄭若華同林鄭月娥會即刻俾人深夜爆門強姦<br />\n就連中聯辦嘅男性職員同所有男性局長都要定期去嗰度開會同輔導<br />\n所以建興大廈一直以來都冇俾人清場嘅原因係因為佢哋就係香港嘅地下維穩最後王牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520aeba4e263b7a9ecf2033ce2596557dcc5e794","tid":2318522,"uid":330057,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:33:15.000Z","msg":"唔講了驚出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46cd0f3d064f236c6bd31d8b7cf44443188a1f9","tid":2318522,"uid":42735,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"你用石頭出糧架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c48a5944492ccff166827730428c7ab0f9fc8d","tid":2318522,"uid":329466,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"建興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？ 連全盛期既樂昌都比唔上"},{"pid":"afd48d4925b5ea030ef51dd8d64ea13d6be68100","tid":2318522,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c46cd0f3d064f236c6bd31d8b7cf44443188a1f9","tid":2318522,"uid":42735,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"你用石頭出糧架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T11:35:39.000Z","msg":"咪撚玩啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\